<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-12] Lustre manuals say almost nothing about interfacing with Windows-in fact the word &quot;windows&quot; does not appear, making finding what is there (i.e., &quot;Samba) very difficult </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-12</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre manuals say almost nothing about interfacing with Windows-in fact the word &quot;windows&quot; does not appear, making finding what is there (i.e., &quot;Samba) very difficult.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
